{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium dynamic Hero section for a Shopify Page template used for service landing pages.
    
    
    
    Use these Shopify page fields dynamically:
    
    Page title as the only H1
    Page content as fallback intro
    Page URL
    
    Use these Page metafields dynamically:
    
    custom.badge_text
    custom.hero_subheading
    custom.hero_image
    custom.hero_image_alt
    custom.primary_cta_text
    custom.primary_cta_link
    custom.secondary_cta_text
    custom.secondary_cta_link
    custom.service_area
    custom.trust_points
    custom.phone_number
    custom.rating_text
    custom.review_count
    custom.target_keywords
    
    Only render each metafield if it has a value.
    
    Design style:
    
    Modern service-business hero
    White background
    Strong red accent #E30613
    Black headings
    Soft grey cards
    Rounded corners 16–24px
    Premium spacing
    Mobile-first
    Fully responsive
    No horizontal scrolling
    Advanced lightweight inline SVG icons
    Looks like a professional local service booking website, not a normal Shopify page
    
    Hero layout:
    
    Desktop:
    
    Left side: badge, H1, hero subheading, service area, rating, trust badges, CTA buttons
    Right side: hero image card and floating quick quote teaser card
    
    Mobile:
    
    Badge, H1, intro, image, CTA buttons, trust badges
    Compact spacing
    Image must appear near the top
    
    Metafield display:
    
    Badge Text as red highlighted badge
    Hero Subheading as rich SEO intro below H1
    Hero Image as main visual
    Hero Image Alt logic:
    {{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title }}
    Service Area as location card with map-pin SVG
    Trust Points as looped pill badges with check SVG
    Rating Text + Review Count as Google-style rating row
    Primary CTA button links to metafield value, fallback #main-quote
    Secondary CTA button links to metafield value, fallback phone number
    Target Keywords should be used only as hidden semantic support or natural context, never shown as ugly keyword stuffing
    
    SEO requirements:
    
    Only one H1: {{ page.title }}
    Use semantic HTML: section, header, h1, p
    Lazy-load hero image
    Use clean alt text
    Keep copy natural and customer-friendly
    Do not keyword stuff
    Make it Google Ads and SEO friendly
    Include basic dynamic WebPage and ImageObject schema if possible using page title, URL, hero image, and hero image alt
    
    Create the full Shopify section file with Liquid, CSS, and JSON schema included.
    Name the section: service-hero
    
    
    white red and black theme , Now enhance and refine this Hero section.
    
    Do not rebuild it. Improve the existing section.
    
    ## Design Improvements
    
    * Make it look like a premium local service business website, not an ecommerce store.
    * Improve spacing, alignment, typography, and visual hierarchy.
    * Add subtle entrance animations and smooth hover effects.
    * Use advanced lightweight inline SVG icons throughout.
    * Increase white space for readability while keeping the hero above the fold.
    * Make the image card feel premium with soft shadow and rounded corners.
    * Add a floating review/rating card overlay on the hero image.
    * Add a floating "Same Day Available" or dynamic badge overlay on the image.
    * Make CTA buttons larger and more prominent.
    * Add a premium trust bar below the hero.
    * Improve mobile responsiveness with no horizontal scrolling.
    * Optimize for Core Web Vitals and fast loading.
    
    ## Dynamic SEO Improvements
    
    Keep everything dynamic using page fields and metafields.
    
    Improve the hero so it naturally supports SEO without keyword stuffing.
    
    Use:
    
    * Page title as the only H1.
    * Hero subheading as the primary SEO introduction.
    * Service area naturally within supporting copy.
    * Target keywords only for semantic context if appropriate.
    * Hero image alt fallback:
      `{{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title }}`
    
    ## Local SEO
    
    Add a dynamic service location row using:
    
    `custom.service_area`
    
    Example:
    
    Serving Sydney CBD, Parramatta, Liverpool, Bankstown and surrounding suburbs.
    
    Do not simply dump keywords.
    
    Write natural, customer-friendly content.
    
    ## Reviews
    
    Display dynamically:
    
    * Rating Text
    * Review Count
    
    Example:
    
    ★★★★★ 5.0 Google Rating • 112 Reviews
    
    If values are empty, hide the block.
    
    ## Trust Points
    
    Loop through:
    
    `custom.trust_points`
    
    Display each as premium icon badges using inline SVG.
    
    ## CTA
    
    Improve button hierarchy.
    
    Primary CTA:
    
    Get Free Quote
    
    Secondary CTA:
    
    Call Now
    
    Buttons should remain dynamic from metafields.
    
    ## Structured Data
    
    Generate dynamic structured data where appropriate using page information.
    
    Include:
    
    * WebPage
    * ImageObject
    * BreadcrumbList
    * LocalBusiness (if available globally)
    
    Do not hardcode schema values.
    
    Use page data and metafields.
    
    ## Accessibility
    
    Improve accessibility:
    
    * Proper heading hierarchy
    * ARIA labels where appropriate
    * Accessible buttons
    * Descriptive image alt text
    * Keyboard-friendly interactions
    
    ## Final Goal
    
    The hero should immediately communicate:
    
    * What service is offered
    * Where the service is available
    * Why customers should trust the business
    * How to request a quote
    
    The final result should feel comparable to a premium service company website, with excellent SEO, mobile usability, and conversion-focused design while remaining lightweight and fully dynamic.
    , Add full dynamic image SEO support using Page metafields.
    
    Add these Page metafields if missing from the section logic:
    
    custom.hero_image
    custom.hero_image_alt
    custom.hero_image_caption
    custom.hero_image_title
    
    Image requirements:
    
    Use custom.hero_image as the main hero image.
    Add dynamic alt text:
    {{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title }}
    Add dynamic image title if available:
    {{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_title.value | default: page.title }}
    Add a visible image caption below the hero image using:
    {{ page.metafields.custom.hero_image_caption }}
    Wrap the image in semantic HTML:
    <figure>, <img>, and <figcaption>.
    Use a clean premium caption style.
    Use lazy loading where appropriate.
    Make the image responsive and mobile-friendly.
    Keep image border radius 16–24px with soft shadow.
    
    Dynamic schema requirements:
    
    Automatically generate ImageObject schema from:
    
    Page title
    Page URL
    Hero image URL
    Hero image alt
    Hero image caption
    Hero image title
    
    Also generate or improve dynamic schema for:
    
    WebPage
    Service
    LocalBusiness if business details are available
    BreadcrumbList
    ImageObject
    
    Use existing Page metafields:
    
    custom.badge_text
    custom.hero_subheading
    custom.service_area
    custom.phone_number
    custom.google_rating
    custom.google_review_count
    custom.target_keywords
    custom.schema_service_type
    custom.schema_area_served
    custom.schema_price_range
    
    Schema must be generated dynamically from page fields and metafields.
    
    Do not require manually pasting JSON-LD into every page.
    
    Do not break if any metafield is empty.
    
    Use conditional Liquid checks.
    
    Image search improvement:
    
    Use the hero image as the primary page image where possible.
    
    If theme files allow it, use the hero image for:
    
    og:image
    twitter:image
    
    If this cannot be done inside this section, add clear comments showing what needs to be added to theme.liquid.
    
    SEO rules:
    
    Do not keyword stuff.
    Use target keywords only naturally.
    Keep the page customer-friendly.
    Use only one H1: {{ page.title }}
    Keep the design clean, fast, mobile-first, and service-business focused.
    
    Final goal:
    
    The hero image should be strongly connected to the page topic for Google Image Search, organic search previews, social sharing, and structured data.
{% enddoc %}
{% liquid
  assign badge_text = page.metafields.custom.badge_text.value
  assign hero_subheading = page.metafields.custom.hero_subheading.value
  assign hero_image = page.metafields.custom.hero_image.value
  assign hero_image_alt = page.metafields.custom.hero_image_alt.value | default: page.title
  assign hero_image_title = page.metafields.custom.hero_image_title.value | default: page.title
  assign hero_image_caption = page.metafields.custom.hero_image_caption.value
  assign primary_cta_text = page.metafields.custom.primary_cta_text.value
  assign primary_cta_link = page.metafields.custom.primary_cta_link.value | default: '#main-quote'
  assign secondary_cta_text = page.metafields.custom.secondary_cta_text.value
  assign secondary_cta_link = page.metafields.custom.secondary_cta_link.value
  assign service_area = page.metafields.custom.service_area.value
  assign trust_points = page.metafields.custom.trust_points.value
  assign phone_number = page.metafields.custom.phone_number.value
  assign rating_text = page.metafields.custom.rating_text.value
  assign review_count = page.metafields.custom.review_count.value
  assign target_keywords = page.metafields.custom.target_keywords.value
  assign schema_service_type = page.metafields.custom.schema_service_type.value
  assign schema_area_served = page.metafields.custom.schema_area_served.value
  assign schema_price_range = page.metafields.custom.schema_price_range.value

  if secondary_cta_link == blank and phone_number != blank
    assign secondary_cta_link = 'tel:' | append: phone_number
  endif

  assign page_description = ''
  if hero_subheading != blank
    assign page_description = hero_subheading | strip_html | truncatewords: 30
  elsif page.content != blank
    assign page_description = page.content | strip_html | truncatewords: 30
  else
    assign page_description = page.title
  endif
%}

{% style %}
  @keyframes service-hero-fade-in-up-{{ section.id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes service-hero-fade-in-{{ section.id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes service-hero-scale-in-{{ section.id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.95);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }

  .service-hero-{{ section.id }} {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #FAFBFC 100%);
    padding: 80px 24px 100px;
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .service-hero-container-{{ section.id }} {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-hero-grid-{{ section.id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .service-hero-content-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
    animation: service-hero-fade-in-up-{{ section.id }} 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .service-hero-badge-{{ section.id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FEE2E2 0%, #FECACA 100%);
    color: #E30613;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    width: fit-content;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.15);
  }

  .service-hero-badge-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .service-hero-h1-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 58px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .service-hero-subheading-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .service-hero-subheading-{{ section.id }} p {
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .service-hero-subheading-{{ section.id }} p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .service-hero-service-area-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    background-color: #F9FAFB;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    max-width: fit-content;
  }

  .service-hero-service-area-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #E30613;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .service-hero-service-area-content-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .service-hero-service-area-label-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6B7280;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .service-hero-service-area-text-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .service-hero-rating-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    background-color: #FFFBEB;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #FDE68A;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .service-hero-stars-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .service-hero-stars-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    color: #F59E0B;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3));
  }

  .service-hero-rating-text-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #92400E;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .service-hero-rating-divider-{{ section.id }} {
    width: 1px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: #FCD34D;
  }

  .service-hero-review-count-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #78350F;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-points-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-badge-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #F0FDF4;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid #BBF7D0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-badge-{{ section.id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
  }

  .service-hero-trust-badge-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #10B981;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-badge-{{ section.id }} span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #065F46;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .service-hero-cta-group-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E30613 0%, #B8050F 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.4);
  }

  .service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }}:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .service-hero-cta-secondary-{{ section.id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 2px solid #000000;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .service-hero-cta-secondary-{{ section.id }}:hover {
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .service-hero-cta-secondary-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .service-hero-visual-{{ section.id }} {
    position: relative;
    animation: service-hero-scale-in-{{ section.id }} 0.9s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .service-hero-image-figure-{{ section.id }} {
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-hero-image-card-{{ section.id }} {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .service-hero-image-card-{{ section.id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-hero-image-caption-{{ section.id }} {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #6B7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-hero-image-overlay-badge-{{ section.id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 24px;
    left: 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E30613 0%, #B8050F 100%);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.4);
    animation: service-hero-fade-in-{{ section.id }} 1s ease-out 0.5s both;
  }

  .service-hero-image-review-card-{{ section.id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 24px;
    right: 24px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    animation: service-hero-fade-in-{{ section.id }} 1s ease-out 0.7s both;
  }

  .service-hero-image-review-stars-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .service-hero-image-review-stars-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    color: #F59E0B;
  }

  .service-hero-image-review-text-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .service-hero-quote-teaser-{{ section.id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30px;
    right: -30px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    max-width: 300px;
    border: 1px solid #F3F4F6;
    animation: service-hero-scale-in-{{ section.id }} 1s ease-out 0.9s both;
  }

  .service-hero-quote-teaser-title-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .service-hero-quote-teaser-text-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #6B7280;
    margin: 0 0 18px 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .service-hero-quote-teaser-cta-{{ section.id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: #E30613;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-hero-quote-teaser-cta-{{ section.id }}:hover {
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .service-hero-quote-teaser-cta-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-bar-{{ section.id }} {
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding: 32px 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F9FAFB 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    animation: service-hero-fade-in-up-{{ section.id }} 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-bar-grid-{{ section.id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-item-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-icon-{{ section.id }} {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E30613 0%, #B8050F 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-icon-{{ section.id }} svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-item-content-{{ section.id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-item-value-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #000000;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .service-hero-trust-item-label-{{ section.id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #6B7280;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .service-hero-keywords-{{ section.id }} {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .service-hero-grid-{{ section.id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
    }

    .service-hero-visual-{{ section.id }} {
      order: -1;
    }

    .service-hero-quote-teaser-{{ section.id }} {
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      max-width: 260px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-hero-{{ section.id }} {
      padding: 48px 20px 60px;
    }

    .service-hero-grid-{{ section.id }} {
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .service-hero-h1-{{ section.id }} {
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    .service-hero-subheading-{{ section.id }} {
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .service-hero-content-{{ section.id }} {
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .service-hero-cta-group-{{ section.id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }},
    .service-hero-cta-secondary-{{ section.id }} {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .service-hero-quote-teaser-{{ section.id }} {
      position: static;
      margin-top: 24px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .service-hero-trust-bar-{{ section.id }} {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }

    .service-hero-trust-bar-grid-{{ section.id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .service-hero-image-overlay-badge-{{ section.id }} {
      top: 16px;
      left: 16px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .service-hero-image-review-card-{{ section.id }} {
      top: 16px;
      right: 16px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<section class="service-hero-{{ section.id }}" {{ section.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="service-hero-container-{{ section.id }}">
    <div class="service-hero-grid-{{ section.id }}">
      <div class="service-hero-content-{{ section.id }}">
        {% if badge_text != blank %}
          <div class="service-hero-badge-{{ section.id }}">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            {{ badge_text }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <h1 class="service-hero-h1-{{ section.id }}">{{ page.title }}</h1>

        {% if hero_subheading != blank %}
          <div class="service-hero-subheading-{{ section.id }}">
            {{ hero_subheading }}
          </div>
        {% elsif page.content != blank %}
          <div class="service-hero-subheading-{{ section.id }}">
            {{ page.content | truncatewords: 30 }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if service_area != blank %}
          <div class="service-hero-service-area-{{ section.id }}">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <div class="service-hero-service-area-content-{{ section.id }}">
              <div class="service-hero-service-area-label-{{ section.id }}">Service Area</div>
              <div class="service-hero-service-area-text-{{ section.id }}">{{ service_area }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if rating_text != blank or review_count != blank %}
          <div class="service-hero-rating-{{ section.id }}" role="img" aria-label="Customer rating: {% if rating_text != blank %}{{ rating_text }}{% endif %}{% if review_count != blank %} based on {{ review_count }} reviews{% endif %}">
            <div class="service-hero-stars-{{ section.id }}" aria-hidden="true">
              {% for i in (1..5) %}
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z" />
                </svg>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% if rating_text != blank %}
              <span class="service-hero-rating-text-{{ section.id }}">{{ rating_text }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            {% if rating_text != blank and review_count != blank %}
              <div class="service-hero-rating-divider-{{ section.id }}"></div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if review_count != blank %}
              <span class="service-hero-review-count-{{ section.id }}">{{ review_count }} reviews</span>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if trust_points != blank %}
          <div class="service-hero-trust-points-{{ section.id }}">
            {% for point in trust_points %}
              <div class="service-hero-trust-badge-{{ section.id }}">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span>{{ point }}</span>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="service-hero-cta-group-{{ section.id }}">
          {% if primary_cta_text != blank %}
            <a href="{{ primary_cta_link }}" class="service-hero-cta-primary-{{ section.id }}" aria-label="{{ primary_cta_text }}">
              {{ primary_cta_text }}
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          {% endif %}

          {% if secondary_cta_text != blank %}
            <a href="{{ secondary_cta_link }}" class="service-hero-cta-secondary-{{ section.id }}" aria-label="{{ secondary_cta_text }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              {{ secondary_cta_text }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-hero-visual-{{ section.id }}">
        <figure class="service-hero-image-figure-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="service-hero-image-card-{{ section.id }}">
            {% if hero_image != blank %}
              <img
                src="{{ hero_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                srcset="{{ hero_image | image_url: width: 400 }} 400w, {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w, {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 800 }} 800w, {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 }} 1200w"
                sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 600px"
                alt="{{ hero_image_alt }}"
                title="{{ hero_image_title }}"
                width="{{ hero_image.width }}"
                height="{{ hero_image.height }}"
                loading="eager"
                fetchpriority="high"
              >
            {% else %}
              {{ 'hero-apparel-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            {% endif %}

            {% if section.settings.show_image_badge and section.settings.image_badge_text != blank %}
              <div class="service-hero-image-overlay-badge-{{ section.id }}">
                {{ section.settings.image_badge_text }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if section.settings.show_image_review and rating_text != blank %}
              <div class="service-hero-image-review-card-{{ section.id }}">
                <div class="service-hero-image-review-stars-{{ section.id }}" aria-hidden="true">
                  {% for i in (1..5) %}
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                      <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z" />
                    </svg>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                <div class="service-hero-image-review-text-{{ section.id }}">{{ rating_text }} Rating</div>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          {% if hero_image_caption != blank %}
            <figcaption class="service-hero-image-caption-{{ section.id }}">
              {{ hero_image_caption }}
            </figcaption>
          {% endif %}
        </figure>

        {% if section.settings.show_quote_teaser %}
          <div class="service-hero-quote-teaser-{{ section.id }}">
            <h2 class="service-hero-quote-teaser-title-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.teaser_title }}</h2>
            <p class="service-hero-quote-teaser-text-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.teaser_text }}</p>
            <a href="{{ section.settings.teaser_link }}" class="service-hero-quote-teaser-cta-{{ section.id }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.teaser_cta_text }}">
              {{ section.settings.teaser_cta_text }}
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    {% if section.settings.show_trust_bar %}
      <div class="service-hero-trust-bar-{{ section.id }}">
        <div class="service-hero-trust-bar-grid-{{ section.id }}">
          <div class="service-hero-trust-item-{{ section.id }}">
            <div class="service-hero-trust-icon-{{ section.id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="service-hero-trust-item-content-{{ section.id }}">
              <div class="service-hero-trust-item-value-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.trust_item_1_value }}</div>
              <div class="service-hero-trust-item-label-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.trust_item_1_label }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="service-hero-trust-item-{{ section.id }}">
            <div class="service-hero-trust-icon-{{ section.id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="service-hero-trust-item-content-{{ section.id }}">
              <div class="service-hero-trust-item-value-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.trust_item_2_value }}</div>
              <div class="service-hero-trust-item-label-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.trust_item_2_label }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="service-hero-trust-item-{{ section.id }}">
            <div class="service-hero-trust-icon-{{ section.id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="service-hero-trust-item-content-{{ section.id }}">
              <div class="service-hero-trust-item-value-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.trust_item_3_value }}</div>
              <div class="service-hero-trust-item-label-{{ section.id }}">{{ section.settings.trust_item_3_label }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  {% if target_keywords != blank %}
    <div class="service-hero-keywords-{{ section.id }}">{{ target_keywords }}</div>
  {% endif %}
</section>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "name": {{ page.title | json }},
      "url": {{ page.url | prepend: request.origin | json }},
      {% if hero_image != blank %}
      "primaryImageOfPage": {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        "url": {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 | json }},
        "width": {{ hero_image.width | json }},
        "height": {{ hero_image.height | json }},
        "caption": {% if hero_image_caption != blank %}{{ hero_image_caption | json }}{% else %}{{ hero_image_alt | json }}{% endif %},
        "name": {{ hero_image_title | json }}
      },
      {% endif %}
      "description": {{ page_description | json }}
    },
    {
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        {
          "@type": "ListItem",
          "position": 1,
          "name": "Home",
          "item": {{ request.origin | json }}
        },
        {
          "@type": "ListItem",
          "position": 2,
          "name": {{ page.title | json }},
          "item": {{ page.url | prepend: request.origin | json }}
        }
      ]
    }
    {% if hero_image != blank %},
    {
      "@type": "ImageObject",
      "url": {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 | json }},
      "width": {{ hero_image.width | json }},
      "height": {{ hero_image.height | json }},
      "caption": {% if hero_image_caption != blank %}{{ hero_image_caption | json }}{% else %}{{ hero_image_alt | json }}{% endif %},
      "name": {{ hero_image_title | json }},
      "contentUrl": {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 | json }},
      "thumbnailUrl": {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 400 | json }}
    }
    {% endif %}
    {% if schema_service_type != blank %},
    {
      "@type": "Service",
      "serviceType": {{ schema_service_type | json }},
      "name": {{ page.title | json }},
      "description": {{ page_description | json }},
      {% if service_area != blank or schema_area_served != blank %}
      "areaServed": {% if schema_area_served != blank %}{{ schema_area_served | json }}{% else %}{{ service_area | json }}{% endif %},
      {% endif %}
      {% if schema_price_range != blank %}
      "priceRange": {{ schema_price_range | json }},
      {% endif %}
      {% if hero_image != blank %}
      "image": {{ hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 | json }},
      {% endif %}
      "provider": {
        "@type": "LocalBusiness",
        "name": {{ shop.name | json }},
        {% if phone_number != blank %}
        "telephone": {{ phone_number | json }},
        {% endif %}
        {% if service_area != blank or schema_area_served != blank %}
        "areaServed": {% if schema_area_served != blank %}{{ schema_area_served | json }}{% else %}{{ service_area | json }}{% endif %},
        {% endif %}
        {% if schema_price_range != blank %}
        "priceRange": {{ schema_price_range | json }},
        {% endif %}
        {% if rating_text != blank and review_count != blank %}
        "aggregateRating": {
          "@type": "AggregateRating",
          "ratingValue": {{ rating_text | json }},
          "reviewCount": {{ review_count | json }}
        },
        {% endif %}
        "url": {{ request.origin | json }}
      }
    }
    {% endif %}
  ]
}
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Service hero",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Image overlays"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_image_badge",
      "label": "Show image badge",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "image_badge_text",
      "label": "Badge text",
      "default": "Same Day Available"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_image_review",
      "label": "Show review card overlay",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Quick quote teaser card"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_quote_teaser",
      "label": "Show floating quote teaser",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "teaser_title",
      "label": "Teaser title",
      "default": "Get instant quote"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "teaser_text",
      "label": "Teaser text",
      "default": "Free quote in 60 seconds"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "teaser_cta_text",
      "label": "Teaser CTA text",
      "default": "Start now"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "teaser_link",
      "label": "Teaser link"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Trust bar"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_trust_bar",
      "label": "Show trust bar",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "trust_item_1_value",
      "label": "Item 1 value",
      "default": "24/7"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "trust_item_1_label",
      "label": "Item 1 label",
      "default": "Available"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "trust_item_2_value",
      "label": "Item 2 value",
      "default": "Insured"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "trust_item_2_label",
      "label": "Item 2 label",
      "default": "Fully Licensed"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "trust_item_3_value",
      "label": "Item 3 value",
      "default": "5,000+"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "trust_item_3_label",
      "label": "Item 3 label",
      "default": "Happy Customers"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Service hero"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
